Package slotmachine.model.slots

Interface SpinResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<SlotLine>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SpinResultImpl
    public interface SpinResult
extends java.lang.Iterable<SlotLine>
    Supporting interface used in the Further Programming Assignment

    This interface should be implemented as SpinResultImpl and represents the five SlotLine that exist as a result of spinning the 3 wheels.

    The class should provide a single constructor that with the following signature 

    public SpinResultImpl(Wheel wheel1, Wheel wheel2, Wheel wheel3)

    Hint: This class is not complex, requiring a simple constructor and just two even simpler methods (if you use the API effectively).

    Author:
    Ross Nye
    See Also:
    Wheel, SlotLine, SlotMachine.spin(int, int)
